lv f\u00f8lge med at ungene ikke f\u00e5r i seg salmonellainfisert sn\u00f8, is eller annet."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b71463ce97f7e3664b68451d03ca21b28fea436e16fd2470a2e60d07f107ce07"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-09-10T19:35:48.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bare siden \u00e5rsskiftet har 5-6 barnehagebarn i Trondheim f\u00e5tt salmonellasmitte fra sm\u00e5fugl. Folkehelseinstituttet advarer mot \u00e5 ha fuglebrett i barnehager og p\u00e5 lekeplasser."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1193838.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Fuglebrett1"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8a46ba51be670663b08057e754a3e2ad6a195fb1.jpg?5985fdb0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Salmonella-smittet i barnehage -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "8a46ba51be670663b08057e754a3e2ad6a195fb1"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["smitte", "trondheim kommune", "trondheim", "barn", "barnehage", "spise sn\u00f8"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "salmonella typhimurium"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["svein gismervik", "eli sagvik"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1193838.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Fuglebr